      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 51 初九</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 51 初九</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初九：震來虩虩，后笑言啞啞，吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first NINE, undivided, shows its subject, when the movement approaches, looking out and around with apprehension, and afterwards smiling and talking cheerfully. There will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
