      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 51 六三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六三：震蘇蘇，震行无眚。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third six, divided, shows its subject distraught amid the startling movements going on. If those movements excite him to (right) action, there will be no mistake.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
