      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 51 六五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六五：震往來厲，億无喪，有事。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth SIX, divided, shows its subject going and coming amidst the startling movements (of the time), and always in peril; but perhaps he will not incur loss, and find business (which he can accomplish).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="yijing-051-zhen__alignment-007">
